              "free_text": [
                " Three targets (of thicknesses",
                "100-200 ug/cm2) were made using 6Li2WO4 powder and",
                "one target (thickness 20 ug/cm2) was made using 6Li2O",
                "powder and evaporated on tantalum disks (of thickness",
                "0.25 mm and diameter 42 mm)"
